title: 13. Answering Your DMs + Top Esthetics Qs! Pt. 2
description: Hi! In part 2 of our Q+A series we are answering your big questions about esthetics-- from ingredients to avoid to how to know if a career in esthetics is for you! We would love to hear what you think - leave us a comment on Instagram and leave us a review! Looking forward to your feedback!
